    (1, '2025-04-06 10:00:00', 0, '2025-04-06 10:00:00', 0, '手机非常满意！屏幕显示效果很棒，拍照效果也很清晰，运行速度很快，推荐购买！', 'https://zym-qlbm-2005.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_2025-12-04_224407_588.jpg,https://zym-qlbm-2005.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/common.jpg', 128, 5, 1, 'https://zym-qlbm-2005.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_2025-12-04_224407_588.jpg', '张三', 1, 1, 1, 1),
    (2, '2025-04-15 14:00:00', 0, '2025-04-15 14:00:00', 0, '笔记本性能很强，运行大型软件也很流畅，轻薄设计方便携带，电池续航也不错。', 'https://zym-qlbm-2005.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/common.jpg', 86, 5, 1, 'https://zym-qlbm-2005.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/common.jpg', '张三', 2, 2, 2, 1),
    (3, '2025-04-25 11:00:00', 0, '2025-04-25 11:00:00', 0, '沙发质量很好，真皮手感舒适，颜色和图片一致，坐上去很舒服，家人都很喜欢！', 'https://zym-qlbm-2005.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202025-10-23%20234242.png,https://zym-qlbm-2005.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/common.jpg', 156, 5, 1, 'https://zym-qlbm-2005.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/4676.jpg_wh860%20%281%29.jpg', '王五', 4, 4, 4, 3),
    (4, '2025-03-22 16:00:00', 0, '2025-03-22 16:00:00', 0, '四件套面料很舒服，颜色也很漂亮，尺寸标准，性价比高，好评！', NULL, 45, 5, 1, 'https://zym-qlbm-2005.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_2025-12-04_224407_588.jpg', '赵六', 6, 6, 6, 4);
